Join the 5-Day Juice Cleanse Challenge! 🍉🥳🎉🍍💫 It starts soon…sign-up now! Link in bio! 👈🏽✨
•
This is the BEST program to cleanse, rebuild, and restore your health, and the intention for this cleanse is to focus on wellness, healing, transformation, community, and connection. 🥒🥬🍏 There's no better time than now to take care of your health, and I believe that a little more #juicing might just be what we all need right now. 🥕 Whether you want to learn about juicing or dive into a #juice FEAST, this program is for everyone. EVERYONE is welcome to join us. You could even join us and try ONE JUICE A DAY to create better lifestyle choices for yourself. 🙏🏽 I will be covering all topics encompassing #health, #veganism, #fasting, and more. My goal is support a community that uplifts one another through #wellness. 🍊
•
The group challenge includes immediate access to...
💻 7 Days of LIVE Interactive Zoom Calls
📚 2 Juicing e-Books (with Recipes!)
📹 Pre-recorded Loom Tutorial for Beginners
🧘‍♀️ 5 Pre-recorded Daily Motivational Videos
🍒 Bonus Video on How to Break Your Cleanse
📝 Daily Notes with Homework
📍...and more!
•
Sign-up for the challenge now at https://challenge.fullyraw.com/5-day-juice-cleanse-challenge-2021 🎉
•
I can't wait to host and guide you through this journey. The official cleanse starts August 7th, so join now and get ready! Don’t wait until the last minute! 👈🏽 Our first zoom call will be before the start date. I hope to see you there! ✨🍉🥳✨ #fullyraw #vegan #juicecleanse

There are only 30 spots for this intimate retreat, so do not wait to book. There are less than 10 spots remaining. Please read through our website page to see all of the details, information, and itinerary. For serious inquiries, please email retreats@fullyraw.com or simply reserve your spot on the checkout page. Those who know me, know that I love with my @pranamat. The benefits of these sets are so helpful I gifted one to all of my retreat attendees in 2019! The @pranamat is an acupressure and massage set that helps to relieve tension, reduce stress, release back pain, tone skin, and increase circulation.
•
For all my followers, I have the promo code: KRISTINA20 - it gives you 20% off everything! ✨💝✨
•
While there are so many ways to use this set, here are 5 different ways that I am showing you today...
•
1️⃣ Step on it! Give your feet a little massage. The lotus flowers touch all the pressure points on your foot, and in my opinion, this experience is better than getting a reflexology foot massage.
2️⃣ Sit on your thigh or IT band. This helps to loosen and strengthen those side leg muscles, and it also helps to tone the skin by bringing more circulation and by activating the skin and tissues.
3️⃣ Sit on it! Give your booty a little invigoration. Trust me when I say this one is intense!
4️⃣ Place the pillow under your lower-back or underneath your stomach. Stretching over the pillow is one of the best ways to release that intense lower back pain. If you're having tummy issues or simply want to help your digestion, place the pillow under your stomach and breath slowly and deeply.
5️⃣ Lay bare on your back. I recommend for beginners to use a t-shirt.
•
15-20 minutes on your set is all that it takes to experience the benefits and relief of this acupressure set. The whole set is made from the best quality sustainable hemp. It's vegan and eco-friendly and is OEKO-Tex certified.
•
20% off code: KRISTINA20
•
Enjoy my friends! 😘

The secret to making any soup is to blend it in a high-speed blender like a Vitamix for three minutes. It’s enough time to warm the soup but not cook it. 🥦🧅🧄🌶
•
This soup is a perfect comfort recipe for this season, and it honestly tastes better than any corn chowder soup I ever enjoyed. Be sure to use truly fresh coconut milk. It makes a difference! I made my own by blending the meat with the water. 🥥
•
📲 Download my app! The exact recipe is on my YouTube channel as well as on my #FullyRaw #vegan #recipe #app! node.text:
16 YEARS RAW VEGAN TODAY! 🥳🎉🌺🥑🍉✨ I went from being a hyperglycemic, type 2 diabetic 18-year old to a strong, healthy woman…and I’ve never looked back. To say that it’s been 16 years since I’ve consumed meat, dairy, gluten, processed foods, etc. is a bit mind-blowing. 🤯 Still here I am standing, in the best health & shape of my life. This journey has changed me and given me life, and I’m forever grateful. 🙏🏽✨
✨
 I look back and only imagine what my life would be like without this GIFT of knowledge and health freedom. ✨🎁 ✨ While it hasn’t been an overnight transformation, every growth opportunity I’ve encountered has shaped who’ve I am today. 🥭 For those who say that diet or lifestyle choices doesn’t matter, I’m a living testimony THAT THEY DO. Eating plant-based with a rich emphasis on more fruits and vegetables helps you to feel your best, and importantly, helps save animal lives and the planet too. 🐛🌎🦋💕
✨
I’ve learned so much the past 16 years, and what I’ll share with you is this: keep moving forward. Every step you take matters. Start with one #fullyraw #vegan meal a day. Plan. Prepare. Share. Learn to grow your own food and live sustainable. Life compassionately. This is an abundant lifestyle! 🥥 And while it may seem like it’s all about the food...it’s about much more than that—it’s body, mind, and spirit healing. 🌸 To those who’ve been on this journey with me and who have continued to support and encourage me...I love you. THANK YOU! Here’s to another 16 years to come!!! 🥭🍇🍓🥑🍊🍒🍉✨
✨
📸 @cashgotwings
✨
Big announcement coming tomorrow! Be sure to keep watch of my website at www.FullyRaw.com 🍉

node.text:
Something I’ve learned about myself is this: I AM FULLY CAPABLE OF MY OWN HEALING. 🐛🦋💫
•
Understanding my inner workings has forced me to be even MORE UBER conscious of my own self-talk. If it’s not with LOVE, it cannot happen. 🌸 Love is the most powerful healing FORCE of all.
•
I don’t need to call my friends every time something hurts—I do better by first going WITHIN and time to process my emotions. I have the key within myself. 🔑
•
Another thing I’ve learned: sharing too much with your friends without asking is highly inappropriate. It shows a lack of boundaries for their space…and for yours. I’m on my journey to learning better boundaries with myself and with others. 🌊
•
I’ve come to realize we all have the answers within us. 🔑🔑🔑 If we just take a few moments to listen to our intuition & to pay attention to how we are truly feeling, shifts can take place and miracles can happen. 🙏🏽
•
This mentality also gives us permission to take full responsibility over our own emotions, pains, changes, relationships, healing, and more. 🌿
•
We are capable of our own healing. No one else can do it for you. When in doubt go within…the answers are there waiting for you. 🙏🏽🔑💫
•
Wishing you all a peaceful, graceful, and loving weekend. 💗
•

node.text:
HAPPY 2-YEAR BIRTHDAY Koko! 🥳🐶💕✨ We’ve been through some tough times together. If you only knew how many times I was told he might not make it——@fullyrawkoko had over 60 cluster convulsion seizures within the first 2-months I rescued him. But—Koko was determined to LIVE and to have the BEST LIFE ever. 
✨
I rescued him from @helpaws shelter in St. Lucia. Having survived being thrown out of a puppy mill at two weeks old and a dog attack that left him with one eye, a cracked cranial in two areas, and 2 brain hernias, he’s been through his fair share of struggle. He has suffered with seizures and other issues since Cash and I brought him home. With the help of our amazing vets @whvmapet @gcvs and his successful surgeries, he’s been seizure free for months and is officially off his medication. 🙏🏽 He will have the ability to have a long and healthy life (and as normal as possible!!) 😭
✨
It’s been quite the journey with this sweet angel, and he just keeps getting better with time. He’s grown to have the most spunky, playful, and loving personality. He’s got SPIRIT. 💕 I celebrate each and every victory with him. He has LIFE. 💫
✨
I’ve only ever wanted to give him the best life possible. We appreciate all your prayers and support since we’ve rescued him. It means the world to us. 🐶🙏🏽✨
✨
Happy Birthday my baby boy! May we have many more to come! 🥳
✨
P.S. Cash & Koko have the same birthday week (and possibly the same birthday since it’s hard to pinpoint the actual birth date of a rescue). I’ve got two Gemini boys in my life. How did this Pisces girl get so lucky?! 😂💓✨
✨

WE GOT WINGS! 🚁 Cash’s birthday wish was to take an open-door helicopter flight of the island…and so we did! 🦕🏝🚁💫
•
This was by far one of the most magical experiences we’ve had together, and it’s a day we will never forget. 🌊
•
We were in continuous awe of nature and this incredible home we have. 🌎
•
Despite my fear of heights, I found a way to TRUST & relax into the experience and soak up every moment. I had so much fun, I would totally do it again. Doors off and all. 😂🙏🏽🚁
•
These are some of my favorite photos I took with my camera while on the flight. The words “epic” and “majestic” simply don’t do the photos justice—these sights were BREATHTAKING. 🤩
•
Birthday mission complete. 🎉 @cashgotwings even loved the birthday cake I made him afterwards. 🥰
•
We are happy to share these special moments with you! More to come! ♥️🎉🏝🚁💫
•
